# Task 1 - Cafeteria Ordering System

A Python OOP application for restaurant menu management and order processing.

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
  
  Or test individual modules:

python dish.py      # Test dish classes and graph
python order.py     # Test order functionality

Core Features
• Menu Management - Add dishes with category, price, inventory
• Order Processing - Add items, calculate total, print receipt
• Inventory Control - Auto-decrement stock, out-of-stock detection
• Dish Recommendations - Graph-based pairing suggestions

  
OOP Concepts Used
Concept         Implementation
Abstraction    `AbstractDish` base class with abstract methods
Encapsulation   Private `__inventory`, controlled access via methods
Inheritance    `MainDish` and `Drink` extend `Dish`
Polymorphism   `get_final_price()` overridden in subclasses

